column10: Yaŋ aŋakwa mukwa sogok amɨn dakon amɨn madep kabɨ gat Parisi amɨn gat da gen kokwin amɨn kabɨ yoyɨŋba abɨŋ muwukba yaŋ yoyɨwit, "Niaŋ ano? Uŋun amɨn wasok tapmɨmɨ toŋ morapmɨ asak.

Prediction: Amɨn kɨnda yoni mɨni amɨn do nandaŋek paŋpulugosak do nandaŋ uŋun amɨn kɨsɨk kɨsɨk ekwaŋ. Jɨgɨ altaŋ ɨba bɨsapmon Yawe da aŋpulugosak.
Reference: Amɨn kɨnda da tapmɨmni mɨni amɨn pɨndagek paŋpulugosok, uŋun amɨn kɨsɨk kɨsɨk tagɨ asak. Jɨgɨ altaŋ ɨmni bɨsapmon Yawe da pulugaŋ yɨpdɨsak.

Prediction: Amɨn on bɨsapmon ekwaŋ uŋun amɨn yokwisi gɨn. Uŋun Piŋkop dakon pi naŋ asat yaŋ nandaŋek wasok tapmɨmɨ toŋ kɨnda kok do yoŋ. Mani kɨnda dɨma kokdaŋ. Kombɨ amɨn Jona dakon tɨlak naŋgɨn kokdaŋ." Yaŋ yaŋek amɨn kabɨ yopmaŋ degek kɨgɨt.

Reference: Gen on uŋun bamɨsi: Nin uŋun gat kɨsi kaloŋɨ kɨmakgɨmaŋ kaŋ, nin uŋun gat kaloŋɨ egɨpdamaŋ.

Prediction: Nin kalbi 14 kabɨ mudaŋakwan tap ɨdap Mediterenian uŋudon kɨŋek tap binap tawit. Kɨŋek kalbi binap 12 kilok aŋakwan tap wakga dakon pi monjɨ da tap wakga tap kɨdɨpmɨŋ kɨndakon kɨŋ altagɨmaŋ yaŋ nandawit.

Prediction: Nak Pol da bɨsap morapmɨ jikon op do nandagɨm. Mani Sunduk da kosit sopsop aŋnimgut.
Reference: Nin jikon kɨk do nandagɨmaŋ. Nak Pol da jikon kosirɨ morapmɨ kɨk do pini agɨm, mani Sunduk da kosit sopmaŋ nimgut.

Prediction: Nak uŋun do madepsi pasalgɨm. Aŋek kɨmot do nandak nandak agɨm. Aŋek uŋun do butno obɨsi jɨk tosok.
Reference: Nak madepsi pasoldot, aŋek kɨmot do nandɨsat. Aŋek uŋun da aban butno madepsi jɨk tosok.

Prediction: Kɨla amɨn madep da but galak do yo paŋabɨŋ gak da telagɨ yutgokon Jerusalem tosok uŋudon gamɨŋek paŋabɨŋ gamamal.
Reference: Kɨla amɨn madep da yutgo Jerusalem tosok uŋudon abɨŋek gak do but galak do yo paŋabaŋ.

Prediction: Gɨkwem aban gobɨŋni da yaŋ noman taŋek uwal yomɨŋakwan pasal kɨwit.
Reference: Uŋun da aban mal da dɨkdɨkni da yaŋ uwalni yaban pasal kɨwit.

Prediction: Gak asisi mudok mudogɨ mɨni nin do but dasi galak taŋ nimɨsal yaŋ nandɨsat. Gengo bamɨ uŋun kulabɨk dɨma asak. Uŋun kundu da yaŋ tebaisi tosok.
Reference: Gak toktogɨsi nin do but dasi galak taŋ nimɨsal uŋun dakon geni yaŋ teŋteŋaŋ wɨgɨkeŋ. Gak gengo aŋteban aŋek nin tagɨsi paŋpulugosol. Uŋun aŋpak kundu da tebai tosok uŋudeŋ toktogɨsi tokdɨsak.

Prediction: Mɨktɨmɨ mɨktɨmɨ mɨktɨmɨ mɨŋat amɨn kabɨ morap nido kwen wɨgɨk aŋek gen yaŋ paŋteban aŋ? Ae nido ɨsal dogɨn aŋpak yokwi ak do gen yaŋ paŋteban aŋ?
Reference: Mɨŋat amɨn kabɨ morap mɨktɨmɨ mɨktɨmɨ ekwaŋ uŋun nido kwen wɨgɨk ak do gen yaŋ paŋteban aŋ? Mɨŋat amɨnyo uŋun nido ɨsal dogɨn yokwi ak do gen yaŋ paŋteban aŋ?

Prediction: Uŋun da nin manjɨŋ nipgut, do nin kɨla amɨn madep dakon mukwa sogok amɨni dagagɨmaŋ, ae Piŋkop Yesu dakon Datni dakon mukwa sogok amɨni egɨpneŋ. Yesu Kristo dagok dagogɨ mɨni yo morap dakon tɨlɨmni taŋ ɨmɨsak. Uŋun asi.
Reference: Yaŋ aŋek nin uŋun gat amɨn kɨla aneŋ do manjɨŋ nipgut, ae iyɨ dakon Piŋkop ae Datni uŋun dakon oman aneŋ do mukwa sogok amɨni egɨpneŋ do manjɨŋ nipgut. Bɨsap mudok mudogɨ mɨni Yesu Kristo dakon tɨlɨmni ae tapmɨm madepni taŋ ɨmdɨsak. Uŋun asi.

Prediction: Jɨgɨ noman taŋ namɨŋakwan gak do yaŋ teban tok agɨm. Nak yaŋ teban tok sigɨn nandaŋek uŋun paret aŋ gamɨsat, do bɨt kɨlapyo Telagɨ Yut Madepgokon paŋabɨŋ soŋek soŋ gabeŋ.
Reference: Kalɨp jɨgɨ noman taŋ naban paret kɨndap da si soŋ mudogɨ uŋun gam do gen kagano kon da yaŋ teban tok kɨlɨ agɨm. Yaŋ agɨm do on paret gak da yutnon paŋobɨŋek kɨndapmon sokdɨsat.
